<plot>Sixteen-year-old Julie wants to marry her 17-year-old boyfriend Joe, but their friends are all against it. They try to persuade Julie to wait until she's 18, when she will be more mature. At first Julie doesn't want to wait, but soon her friends' stories and examples begin to make her think, and she finally decides to take their advice and wait.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?661301</url></doc>
